data.description: This beautiful and spacious 4 bedroom home is ready for its new owners. Located in the established Rolling Creek subdivision, centrally located and close to award winning schools. This house has been very well take care of, with fresh new paint throughout. It features a large living area and high ceilings. Spacious kitchen with stainless steel appliances and granite countertops. The master bedroom is located downstairs with a full bathroom, and all other bedrooms located upstairs along with a very sizeable game room for entertaining or family movie nights. Almost forgot to mention, no carpet at all! Wood and tile flooring throughout the home. Retreat to the large backyard, perfect for entertaining guests. It also has a sprinkler system, water softener and solar panels already installed.  This is a must see!
